snippet.title: Fist's Elimination Tower: Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Fist's Elimination Tower is opening its door soon! Contestants must the top of this 150-story obstacle course by jumping on all of the robots on each floor within 5 seconds. Customize the contestants, change the way the tower looks, and attempt increasingly tougher challenges. Also, LOOK OUT FOR FISTS!

Coming to Steam and itch.io July 2017. Find out more at http://www.eliminationtower.com
